ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Yes! You might never go to the region, but it's a class through which you can connect China with the rest of the world so far back in history.
it is good for any students who want to study history and work on original documents
Yes I would recommend it to other students, especially if she/he is interested in working with unconventional sources in historical studies.
Although readings are heavy, I would recommend this for anyone interested in East Asian and world history. Knowledge of Chinese is helpful.

narratives.question_text: How did this course deepen your knowledge of your discipline/profession? To what extent did this course contribute to your dissertation/research?
comments: gives me a good training in history discipline
This course has prepared me for future research with manuscripts.
